{
  "texts": [
    "Just like widely used predictive tools based on statistical learning (Buolamwini and Gebru, 2018), LLMs could harbor massive social biases (Bender et al., 2021).",
    "Together, these elements cast a shadow over LLMs' ability to effectively mimic diverse human populations in survey simulations.",
    "While they might represent some groups properly, they may be failing others.",
    "We label this view the \"social bias hypothesis.\"",
    "3 In this article, we propose a third alternative."
  ]
}